title: Issa Rae | Impressions Nobody Asked For
description:
Seth shares some of his writers' obscure celebrity impressions that nobody asked for, like Clarice Starling from The Silence of the Lambs.

Then, he talked to Issa Rae of the new movie The Lovebirds.
